text: "My Head & My Heart" is a dance/pop song by Ava Max, released on November 19, 2020. It is from her debut album, Heaven & Hell. The song samples ATC's 2000 debut single "Around the World (La La La La La)". Commercially, the song reached the top 10 in 10 countries.
